---

<InfoLayout title="Nicodes | Portfolio">
  <h2>My Work</h2>

  <FlexGrid>
    <Fragment slot="left">
      <Section>
        <p>
          Here's a list of my creations. Each has a brief description and don't
          miss out on the embedded demos!
        </p>

        <p>To learn more please <a>reach out</a>!</p>
      </Section>

      <Section>
        <h3>Pink Sofa Hour</h3>

        <IframeBrowser src="https://pinksofahour.com" />

        <p>
          <a href="https://pinksofahour.com">Pink Sofa Hour</a> is a YouTube show/podcast
          featuring local musical artists in Boulder CO. This site is built with
          multiple capabilities including YouTube, Google Calendar, and SMTP integration.
        </p>

        <div class={styles.coreTech}>
          <p>Core technologies:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Astro</li>
            <li>TypeScript</li>
            <li>Google Drive API</li>
            <li>Google Calendar API</li>
            <li>YouTube API</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p>Checkout the code on <a>GitHub</a></p>
      </Section>

      <Section>
        <h3>CT Calc</h3>

        <IframeBrowser src="https://www.ctcalc.com" />

        <p>
          <a href="https://www.ctcalc.com">CT Calc</a> is used to provide contact
          time inactivation of Giardia and viruses for several disinfectants. These
          calculations can be useful for determining compliance with EPA guidelines.
        </p>

        <div class={styles.coreTech}>
          <p>Core technologies:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Astro</li>
            <li>HTMX</li>
            <li>TypeScript</li>
            <li>Python</li>
            <li>Vercel</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p>Checkout the code on <a>GitHub</a></p>
      </Section>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="right">
      <Section>
        <h3>Schlop Stop</h3>

        <IframeBrowser src="https://www.schlopstop.com" />

        <p>
          <a href="https://www.schlopstop.com">Schlop Stop</a> is a food truck based
          in Boulder CO. I used AI tools to design the logo and built this site to
          host their menu. It also includes Google Drive support to update the menu
          in real time. More additions are cooking up!
        </p>

        <div class={styles.coreTech}>
          <p>Core technologies:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Astro</li>
            <li>TypeScript</li>
            <li>Google Drive API</li>
            <li>Vercel</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p>Checkout the code on <a>GitHub</a></p>
      </Section>

